column5: Well I went down that way to muskie fish sat but way too rough to get on st clair.   So I launched out of wheatley and tryed bass on erie.  Couldn;t find  structure or rocks anywhere out there. Gps showed humps and stuff at pellee point on the gps but didn;t move a fish.  Where do they find bass out there is my question
So close, you went east and should have went South West. Next time head out of Colchester, strait out a mile and you will be on a great piece of structure that will land you some NICE smallies.
